node.text:
Happy Birthday @brandon_c_sears !  Thank you for being such an awesome person to look up to throughout my life.  Brandon has inspired many in the skimming world and me just being one of the few.  As a kid I always wanted to do Skim airs like him.  Now we fly in the air together.  Happy Birthday legend!  Too many more skim sessions together!
